h2. HTML\n
\n
Some block layouts are simply textile versions of HTML tags with the same name, like @div@, @pre@, and @p@. HTML tags can also exist on their own line:\n
\n
<section>\n
  <h1>Title</h1>\n
  <p>Hello!</p>\n
